{"tid":2488054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁天琦政治能量　香港其他政治人物難以比擬，遑論那些投機之徒","createTime":"2021-04-14T03:38:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T05:41:18.000Z","uid":261647,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"7ab78412d116c7f3df5e66244b22dfacdac456b3","tid":2488054,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:38:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ISJYCH/posts/10158036385393034\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FISJYCH%2Fposts%2F10158036385393034&d=t2%2FAN0mLur8%2Bj%2B1TvbkzviUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=db485085\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ISJYCH/posts/10158036385393034</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：袁志豪<br />\n<br />\n梁天琦之所以能把不同世代、不同出身、不同光譜的人連結在一起，是天時（本土派未被理解之時）、地利（非香港出生）、人和（知行合一地實踐了其論述）互相結合的結果。<br />\n<br />\n理解到這一點，你便知道為何他所產生的政治能量，是香港其他政治人物（無論是過去還是現在）所難以比擬的，更遑論那些投機之徒。"},{"pid":"83c8c8874cdff3393a5f87e9c5731c25696f84df","tid":2488054,"uid":66087,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:42:24.000Z","msg":"非香港出生係地利? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb242b5a1c8e0a40296adb065d63312ba8ba9a55","tid":2488054,"uid":228143,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:42:43.000Z","msg":"唔講投唔投機先<br />\n<br />\n袁爸 郭文貴果d出來係做咩鬼<br />\n<br />\n冇次中又9唔搭8負資產來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0184ffa92b59b6a7cd8d2ab2f599fda4a6b7753e","tid":2488054,"uid":93986,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T03:42:50.000Z","msg":"真 咁多個政治人物 只會信佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e2b84c218dad772f16ded9a242a77eb7500a21a","tid":2488054,"uid":37525,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T04:00:41.000Z","msg":"梁繼平呢咁？"},{"pid"